<h2>4.5 UpdateProjectRequestDto Class</h2>

<p><b>Description:</b> DTO for updating an existing project request. Extends PartialType(CreateProjectRequestDto), making all fields from the create DTO optional. Adds an additional status field.</p>

<h3>Class Attributes</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>No</th><th>Attribute</th><th>Type</th><th>Validators</th><th>Description</th></tr>
