<tr><td>02</td><td>status</td><td>RequestStatus (optional)</td><td>@IsOptional()</td><td>Allows explicitly setting the request status (e.g., PUBLIC_DRAFT, PRIVATE_DRAFT, PENDING_SPECS). Optional.</td></tr>
</table>

