</tr>
<tr>
  <td>04</td>
  <td>getQuestion(code: string): WizardQuestion or undefined</td>
  <td>Helper that finds a wizard question object by its code (e.g., 'PRODUCT_TYPE', 'INDUSTRY', 'FEATURES').</td>
</tr>
