<p><b>Description:</b> Centralized Axios wrapper class providing HTTP methods with automatic authentication (httpOnly cookies), token refresh with single-flight deduplication, session reconciliation for multi-tab scenarios, and timezone header injection.</p>

<h3>Class Attributes</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>No</th><th>Attribute</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr>
