<tr><td>02</td><td>refreshPromise</td><td>Promise&lt;void&gt; or null</td><td>Single-flight lock for token refresh to prevent concurrent refresh calls.</td></tr>
<tr><td>03</td><td>sessionReconcilePromise</td><td>Promise&lt;void&gt; or null</td><td>Single-flight lock for session reconciliation across tabs.</td></tr>
<tr><td>04</td><td>isRedirectingToLogin</td><td>boolean</td><td>Flag to prevent duplicate login redirects.</td></tr>
<tr><td>05</td><td>lastLoginTime</td><td>number</td><td>Timestamp of last login, used to avoid premature refresh after login.</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>Class Methods</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>No</th><th>Method</th><th>Description</th></tr>
<tr><td>01</td><td>async get&lt;T&gt;(url, config?): Promise&lt;T&gt;</td><td>Sends GET request, returns response.data.</td></tr>
<tr><td>02</td><td>async post&lt;T&gt;(url, data?, config?): Promise&lt;T&gt;</td><td>Sends POST request with body, returns response.data. Used by wizardService.submitRequest().</td></tr>
<tr><td>03</td><td>async patch&lt;T&gt;(url, data?, config?): Promise&lt;T&gt;</td><td>Sends PATCH request, returns response.data. Used by wizardService.updateRequest().</td></tr>
<tr><td>04</td><td>setupInterceptors(): void</td><td>Configures request interceptor (timezone header, FormData handling) and response interceptor (401 handling with token refresh). Private method.</td></tr>
<tr><td>05</td><td>async refreshAccessTokenSingleFlight(): Promise&lt;void&gt;</td><td>Performs token refresh via POST /auth/refresh with deduplication to avoid race conditions. Private method.</td></tr>
</table>

